uvad — standalone extraction of the UniMRCP activity detector

This directory contains code derived from the UniMRCP Project
(http://www.unimrcp.org), specifically:

  libs/mpf/src/mpf_activity_detector.c
  libs/mpf/include/mpf_activity_detector.h

